-- Nigerian Security Chief Sees Boko Haram Government Link, FT Says
-- B y   S a r a h   S h a n n o n
-- 2012-02-11T09:43:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-11/nigerian-security-chief-sees-boko-haram-government-link-ft-says.html
The Islamist group Boko Haram has
links inside  Nigeria ’s government and may attack previously safe
parts of the nation, the Financial Times reported, citing the
country’s national security adviser.  General Owoye Azazi said attacks by the group, which killed
hundreds of people in the last year, may happen anywhere and
Boko Haram might have obtained assistance from al-Qaeda in the
Maghreb, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
